import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Press Win+R to open Run dialog
    pyautogui.hotkey('win', 'r')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Type notepad and press Enter
    pyautogui.typewrite('notepad')
    time.sleep(0.2)
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(1)
    print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
except Exception as e:
    print("FAILED: " + str(e))
